OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,FBowen Cole from is half Welsh and half
OL,8,FRwandan. He is aged 17, and believes
OL,9,FRwanda has been judged unfairly
OL,10,Fbecause of the UK Government's plan to
OL,11,Fdeport failed asylum seekers there.
OL,13,FAlmost two years after the UK and
OL,14,FRwanda signed an agreement for the UK
OL,15,Fto deport people seeking asylum in
OL,16,FBritain to Rwanda, the debate over the
OL,17,Fsuitability of the country as such a
OL,18,Fdestination rages.
