OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,FThe Welsh language current affairs
OL,8,Fprogramme, Y Byd ar Bedwar, travelled
OL,9,Fto Rwanda with Bowen to understand
OL,10,Fmore about the country at the centre
OL,11,Fof the scheme.
OL,13,F"I can see there's a stigma with
OL,14,FRwanda now, and it makes me so
OL,15,Ffrustrated because this is such a
OL,16,Fgood, peaceful country," said Bowen.
