OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,F"If (asylum seekers) are sent to
OL,8,FRwanda, nothing is going to happen (to
OL,9,Fthem), nothing bad is going to happen.
OL,10,FThey are going to be treated like
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,F"I believe there are quite a few
OL,14,Fsimilarities between Rwanda and Wales,
OL,15,Ffor example the majority of people
OL,16,Fundermine Wales and Rwanda, they think
OL,17,Fthey know these countries, but they
OL,18,Fdon't."
