OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,FSince the government plans were
OL,8,Fannounced, Bowen says he has
OL,9,Fexperienced judgement over his
OL,10,Fheritage.
OL,12,F"When I say I'm from Rwanda, people
OL,13,Fstart to question me.
OL,15,F"I never thought I'd live to see the
OL,16,Fday that I'm judged for coming from
OL,17,FRwanda."
