OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,FUnder the agreement, designed to deter
OL,8,Fpeople from arriving in the UK on
OL,9,Fsmall boats, some asylum seekers would
OL,10,Fbe sent to Rwanda to have their claims
OL,11,Fprocessed there.
OL,13,FIf their claims are successful, they
OL,14,Fwill be granted refugee status and
OL,15,Fallowed to stay in Rwanda. If their
OL,16,Fclaims are unsuccessful, they could
OL,17,Fapply to settle in Rwanda on other
OL,18,Fgrounds, or seek asylum in another
OL,19,F"safe third country".
