OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,FBowen has mixed feelings about the
OL,8,Fpolicy.
OL,10,F"I come from Wales, and I come from
OL,11,FRwanda... if I say I'm against the
OL,12,Fpolicy, people will think I hate
OL,13,FRwanda, but, God forbid, I don't.
OL,15,F"(But) I'm against the policy, because
OL,16,Fif the (migrants) want to go to the
OL,17,FUK, let them go to the UK.
