OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,F"How would you feel if you ran away
OL,8,Ffrom your war-torn country, to a
OL,9,Fcountry you thought would be safe,
OL,10,Fjust to be turned away?"
OL,12,FHowever, Bowen says if the plan goes
OL,13,Fahead, those sent to Rwanda have
OL,14,Fnothing to fear.
OL,16,F"If anyone knows how to take care of
OL,17,Fmigrants, knows what they want, and
OL,18,Ftreats them like people - it's Rwanda."
