OL,7,FConcerns have been raised regarding
OL,8,FRwanda's ability to accept more
OL,9,Frefugees.
OL,11,FAs of the end of September 2023,
OL,12,FRwanda hosted 135,733 refugees, asylum
OL,13,Fseekers and other displaced
OL,14,Fpopulations. A third of those come
OL,15,Ffrom Burundi, a country which shares
OL,16,Fits border with Rwanda.
