OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,FA refugee who arrived in Rwanda from
OL,8,FBurundi in 2015 told Y Byd ar Bedwar
OL,9,Fthat he still hasn't been able to find
OL,10,Fa job. His identity has been concealed
OL,11,Fto protect his safety.
OL,13,F"It's hard to find a job, I've been
OL,14,Ftrying for years," he said. "Many
OL,15,Fpeople want you to work for free, and
OL,16,Fthey say they'll pay you later, but
OL,17,Fit's impossible. Finding a job is
OL,18,Fdifficult.
