OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,F"I get some part-time jobs... it
OL,8,Fprovides me with some small income to
OL,9,Fhelp me survive."
OL,11,FHe said it took him two years to
OL,12,Freceive refugee status in the country,
OL,13,Fa process the Rwandan Government says
OL,14,Fshould only take two months.
OL,16,F"When you arrive in Rwanda, you are
OL,17,Fgiven accommodation such as a tent you
OL,18,Fcan live in... and then they
OL,19,Finvestigate you to ensure you are a
OL,20,Freal refugee.
