OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,F"It took about two years for the whole
OL,8,Fprocess to be completed, and for me to
OL,9,Fbe registered as an official refugee.
OL,11,F"It wasn't easy, it was a difficult
OL,12,Fperiod. I cried a lot... I still think
OL,13,Fabout the situation and I feel sad,
OL,14,Fbut I have to accept it."
