OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,FAsylum seekers who go to Rwanda from
OL,8,Fthe UK would have a roof over their
OL,9,Fheads at Hope Hostel, a hotel in north
OL,10,FKigali, the capital city of Rwanda.
OL,11,FThere's room for 100 people there, and
OL,12,Fthe Rwandan government says they would
OL,13,Fstay there for three months before
OL,14,Fmoving to more permanent accommodation.
OL,16,FLilly Carlisle works for the United
OL,17,FNations Refugee Agency (UNHCR) in
OL,18,FRwanda. She's been supporting refugees
OL,19,Fin the country for two years.
