OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,F"It's a protracted crisis, the
OL,8,Frefugees have been here for 10 years
OL,9,Fplus," she said. "Finding a job is
OL,10,Ftough. Around 80-90% of refugees here
OL,11,Fare completely dependent on
OL,12,Fhumanitarian assistance."
OL,14,FLilly believes sending more asylum
OL,15,Fseekers to Rwanda would pose serious
OL,16,Frisks for the safety of refugees.
