OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,F"This is shifting the burden,
OL,8,Fessentially, from the UK to Rwanda. We
OL,9,Fthink the UK should take
OL,10,Fresponsibility for these asylum
OL,11,Fseekers in assessing their claims
OL,12,Frather than shifting the
OL,13,Fresponsibility to a country like
OL,14,FRwanda who already has a lot to deal
OL,15,Fwith with the existing refugee
OL,16,Fpopulation.
