OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,F"You will have, essentially, two
OL,8,Fdifferent systems dealing with asylum
OL,9,Fseekers and refugees in the same
OL,10,Fcountry. Right now, we do not consider
OL,11,Fthe asylum system safe to bring more
OL,12,Fpeople here."
