OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,FThe UK Government's plan to send some
OL,8,Fasylum seekers to Rwanda has faced
OL,9,Fmany legal challenges. The UK Supreme
OL,10,FCourt ruled unanimously in November
OL,11,F2023 that the Rwanda scheme was
OL,12,Funlawful. It said genuine refugees
OL,13,Fsent there would be at risk of being
OL,14,Freturned to their home countries,
OL,15,Fwhere they could face harm.
OL,17,FDr Doris Uwicyeza Picard, chief
OL,18,Ftechnical advisor for the Rwanda
OL,19,FMinistry of Justice, said there is "no
OL,20,Fsuch risk for any asylum seekers, not
OL,21,Fjust those relocated from the UK".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/23
