OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,FDr Picard was a part of the team
OL,8,Fresponsible for discussing the terms
OL,9,Fof the agreement with the UK
OL,10,FGovernment, and she played a key role
OL,11,Fin drafting the legal framework for
OL,12,Fthe plan.
OL,14,F"We have scaled up (processes) because
OL,15,Fnow we expect an increase in asylum
OL,16,Fapplications, we've scaled up
OL,17,Fcapacity, we are reforming our entire
OL,18,Fasylum process.
