OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,F"We understand that there (were)
OL,8,Fconcerns that were expressed by the
OL,9,FSupreme Court and those have been
OL,10,Faddressed."
OL,12,FResponding to the lack of jobs in the
OL,13,Fcountry, Dr Picard said" "Unemployment
OL,14,Fis an issue everywhere and this is
OL,15,Fwhere we believe that migration is
OL,16,Fwealth that is being brought into the
OL,17,Fcountry because we're bringing in
OL,18,Fwealth of experience and education and
OL,19,Fskills.
