OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,F"The more people there are, the more
OL,8,Fjobs there are. There are not just job
OL,9,Fopenings waiting for people to fill
OL,10,Fthem, a job is created by the people."
OL,12,FWhen challenged on the length of time
OL,13,Fit takes for asylum seekers to receive
OL,14,Frefugee status, Dr Picard said: "It
OL,15,Fusually takes on average two months to
OL,16,Fget your residence, to get the refugee
OL,17,Fstatus."
