OL,7,FIn response to the Supreme Court's
OL,8,Fruling in November that the Rwanda
OL,9,Fscheme was unlawful, the UK Government
OL,10,Fintroduced a new bill to make clear in
OL,11,FUK law that Rwanda is a safe country.
OL,12,FThe legislation must be approved by
OL,13,Fboth Houses of Parliament, however the
OL,14,FLords defeated it in early March.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G20/23
