OL,3,C'I'm half Welsh and half Rwandan `
OL,4,Cthis is why I'm against the Rwanda
OL,5,CPlan'
OL,7,FOpponents of the plan are concerned it
OL,8,Fplaces the UK at risk of breaching
OL,9,Finternational law commitments,
OL,10,Fundermines the jurisdiction of the
OL,11,Fcourts, will lead to substantial
OL,12,Ftaxpayer costs, fails to provide safe
OL,13,Fand legal routes for refugees and does
OL,14,Fnot include measures to tackle people
OL,15,Fsmugglers.
OL,17,FThe bill has returned to the Commons
OL,18,Ffor considerations of Lords amendments
OL,19,Fon Monday, 18 March.
