OL,7,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "As
OL,8,Fthe home secretary and prime minister
OL,9,Fhave said, we remain committed to
OL,10,Fgetting flights to Rwanda off the
OL,11,Fground once the bill and treaty are in
OL,12,Fplace.
OL,14,F"We have a strong relationship with
OL,15,Fthe Rwandans and will continue to work
OL,16,Fclosely with them to operationalise
OL,17,Fthe policy."
